import org.apache.spark.input.PortableDataStream
import java.util.zip.ZipInputStream
import java.io.BufferedReader
import java.io.InputStreamReader


def RDDDownloader(fileName: String): org.apache.spark.rdd.RDD[String] = 
{
    val resultRDD = sc.binaryFiles(fileName). // charger quelques fichers via une regex
    flatMap {  // decompresser les fichiers
       case (name: String, content: PortableDataStream) =>
          val zis = new ZipInputStream(content.open)
          Stream.continually(zis.getNextEntry).
                takeWhile(_ != null).
                flatMap { _ =>
                    val br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zis))
                    Stream.continually(br.readLine()).takeWhile(_ != null)
                }
    }
    return resultRDD
}

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
val mentions_tri = mentions_bis.select($"GLOBALEVENTID" , $"MentionDocTone", substring(col("MentionDocTranslationInfo"), 7, 3).as("language"))
val joined_df = events_bis.select($"GLOBALEVENTID", $"MonthYear", $"Actor1Name", $"Actor2Name",$"Actor1Code", $"Actor2Code", $"ActionGeo_CountryCode").join(mentions_tri, Seq("GLOBALEVENTID"), "inner")
val newDf1 = joined_df.withColumn("Positive", when( $"MentionDocTone">0, $"MentionDocTone").otherwise(0))
val newDf2 = newDf1.withColumn("Negative", when( $"MentionDocTone"<0,  $"MentionDocTone").otherwise(0))
val df_actor1 = newDf2.filter( "Actor1Name != ''").withColumn("ActorCode", $"Actor1Code").withColumn("ActorName", $"Actor1Name").drop("Actor1Name").drop("Actor2Name").drop("Actor1Code").drop("Actor2Code")
val df_actor2 = newDf2.filter( "Actor2Name != ''").withColumn("ActorCode", $"Actor2Code").withColumn("ActorName", $"Actor2Name").drop("Actor1Name").drop("Actor2Name").drop("Actor1Code").drop("Actor2Code")
val df_fin = df_actor1.union(df_actor2)
val df_query3 = df_fin.groupBy("GLOBALEVENTID",  "MonthYear",  "ActionGeo_CountryCode", "language", "ActorCode", "ActorName").agg(sum("Positive").as("Positive"),sum("Negative").as("Negative"))
print(df_actor1.count())
print(df_actor2.count())
print(df_fin.count())

z.show(sql("""
     SELECT tab.actor, sum( tab.Positive) as Positive, sum(tab.Negative) as Negative
     FROM (
     (
        SELECT Actor1Code AS actor, SUM(CASE WHEN AvgTone>0 Then AvgTone Else 0 End) AS Positive, SUM(CASE WHEN AvgTone<0 Then AvgTone Else 0 End) AS Negative
        FROM events 
        WHERE Actor1Code != ''
        AND  MonthYear = 201802
        GROUP BY Actor1Code
     ) 
     UNION 
     (
        SELECT Actor2Code AS actor, SUM(CASE WHEN AvgTone>0 Then AvgTone Else 0 End) AS Positive, SUM(CASE WHEN AvgTone<0 Then AvgTone Else 0 End) AS Negative
        FROM events 
        WHERE Actor2Code != ''
        AND  MonthYear = 201802
        GROUP BY Actor2Code
     )) as tab
     GROUP BY tab.actor
     ORDER BY Positive DESC
     """))
